{"tid":1675583,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"華迪：以為可以贏10球！","createTime":"2019-10-26T03:57:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-28T13:37:55.000Z","uid":252013,"like":36,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"bc3bf2dd66f9ca626e559cce5f20743bcc8de4e3","tid":1675583,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:57:09.000Z","msg":"9:0真係太誇張...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n李斯特城今仗於多踢1人之下，打出水銀瀉地的進攻足球，最終華迪和艾約斯佩雷斯各自射入3球，加上芝維爾、泰利文斯及占士麥迪臣各建一功，以9:0摧毀修咸頓。華迪於賽後道：「當下半場艾約斯射成6:0後，莊尼伊雲斯對我們說，如果我們繼續入球，或許可以打破曼聯的紀錄。」<br />\n「所以我們傾力入球，深信可以做得到。這是一場足以令球迷驕傲的勝仗，球員表現一流。我們知道當你少打1人，就會十分難踢，再加上我們狀態很好，知道可以為對手製造麻煩。」(<a href=\"http://goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoal.com&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=30715232\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goal.com</a>)<br />\n...<a href=\"https://ball.klwpc.com/share.php?a=ballwwl&amp;id=16264\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fball.klwpc.com%2Fshare.php%3Fa%3Dballwwl%26id%3D16264&d=fqbTeswMZLFOgVdkXXOtN8bSs98ObMNNw7VTZDCdQw4%3D&h=d28ec332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ball.klwpc.com/share.php?a=ballwwl&amp;id=16264</a>"},{"pid":"4228950286f2bf823b4e58c1470c42c45827d55e","tid":1675583,"uid":21969,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:58:30.000Z","msg":"踢fifa 咁撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b8c847ff87b6fbe0f37327f9e54e7459e6368e5","tid":1675583,"uid":4179,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T03:58:47.000Z","msg":"羅渣back<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a2d046d3cb3f4ab95d71f38749d3482d6b9b27","tid":1675583,"uid":30040,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-10-26T04:04:12.000Z","msg":"華dee其實真係